# Developer override configs are gitignored but `COPY . .` still picks them
# up from the local working tree; boiler loads them at higher precedence
# than the operator's --config file, so a stray copy shadows wizard-set
# service identity in the running container. CI builds run on a clean
# checkout and are unaffected; this guard protects local docker builds
# (rc-build-and-push.sh, ad-hoc `docker build .` iterations).
**/override-config.yml
